            <title><![CDATA[Juufuutei Raden’s Guide for Pixel Museum DLC ‘Hakone Travelogue’ announced]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gematsu.com/2026/05/juufuutei-radens-guide-for-pixel-museum-dlc-hakone-travelogue-announced</link>
            <guid>1522618</guid>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div id="readability-page-1" class="page"><div><p>Jupiter Corporation has announced pixel puzzle game <em>Juufuutei Raden’s Guide for Pixel Museum</em> downloadable content “Hakone Travelogue.” It will launch in December. <span id="more-1048100"></span></p><p>Here is an overview of the downloadable content, via <a title="Companies > Jupiter Corporation [34 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/jupiter-corporation">Jupiter Corporation</a>:</p><blockquote><p><strong>About</strong></p><p>We are opening a new event exhibit, themed around Curator Raden’s beloved region of Hakone! Indulge in the charm of Hakone with this pack of Pixel Puzzles that feature its places of interest, wor ks of art, and more.</p><p><strong>Key Features</strong></p><ul><li>30 Hakone-themed Pixel Puzzles (including special themes available in collaboration with art museums and businesses!).</li><li>Three Memories of Raden Pixel Puzzles.</li><li>Additional background music tracks featured in the memories.</li><li>New commentary voiceovers for all works.</li></ul><!-- AD: content -->
        </blockquote><p><em><a title="Games > Juufuutei Raden's Guide for Pixel Museum [4 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/juufuutei-radens-guide-for-pixel-museum">Juufuutei Raden’s Guide for Pixel Museum</a></em> is available now for <a title="Platforms > PS4 [28,737 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps4">PlayStation 4</a>, <a title="Platforms > Xbox Series [8,796 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-series">Xbox Series</a>, <a title="Platforms > Xbox One [14,418 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-one">Xbox One</a>, <a title="Platforms > Switch [18,382 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch">Switch</a>, and <a title="Platforms > PC [25,613 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a> via <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/3204020/Juufuutei_Radens_Guide_for_Pixel_Museum/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Steam</a> and <a href="https://www.microsoft.com/store/productid/9p34wqxs0hv5" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Microsoft Store</a>.</p><p>Watch the announcement trailer below. View a set of screenshots <a href="https://www.gematsu.com/gallery/juufuutei-radens-guide-for-pixel-museum/may-17-2026/">at the gallery</a>.</p><h2><span>Announce Trailer</span></h2><p><iframe title="追加DLC『儒烏風亭らでんがご案内！ピクセルミュージアム ―箱根探訪編―』ティザー映像（2026/5）" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/iSZfNJc0BDs?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p><h2><span>Screenshots</span></h2><div id="carousel_1048102"><ul><li><span>❮</span></li><li><span>❯</span></li></ul></div></div></div><br/><br/>https://www.gematsu.com/2026/05/juufuutei-radens-guide-for-pixel-museum-dlc-hakone-travelogue-announced]]></content:encoded>
